# .todo/.tip

> **Rule: Every todo entry must have a corresponding `.tip` file (e.g., `feature.tip`). No todo should exist without its `.tip`.**

This file is now a placeholder. Each todo now has its own `.tip` file (e.g., `migration.tip`, `project_normalization.tip`) to enable parallel agent work and avoid conflicts.

See individual `.tip` files for current progress and next steps for each todo.
